headline: JPMorgan Almost At This Crucial Chart Level As Earnings Help Extend Rebound
summary: JPMorgan Chase is the IBD Stock of the Day as the stock approaches a buy point and banking stocks in general extend rebounds.  JPMorgan stock is on pace to climb three of the past four weeks, and it has wiped out big losses that started April 3 with the announcement of sweeping import tariffs.  With assets of $3.9 trillion, JPMorgan is the nation's largest bank.
